{"word":"G4225 - πού - poú - poo - About","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πού</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">poú</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">poo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">About</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஏறக்குறைய, ஒருஇடத்தில் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. somewhere"},{"paragraph":"2. nearly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Genitive case of <b>&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C2;</b> <b>pos</b>, an indefinite pronoun  (<i>some</i>) otherwise obsolete (compare <a href=\"#/G4214 - πόσος - pósos - pos'-os/4214\">G4214</a>); as adverb of place, <i>somewhere</i>, that is, <i>nearly:</i> - about, a certain place.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}